section.section:
The appropriate governing body shall calculate the amount of the tax credit under this section equal to a percentage of the amount of property tax imposed on the eligible assessment of the qualified property, as follows:
80% in each of the 1st 5 taxable years following the calendar year in which the property initially becomes a qualified property;
70% in the 6th taxable year;
60% in the 7th taxable year;
50% in the 8th taxable year;
40% in the 9th taxable year; and
30% in the 10th taxable year.
